# 👋 Hey, I'm Harsh Khatri
### AI/ML Engineer | Cloud Enthusiast | Problem Solver
---

## 💫 About Me

I'm an AI/ML Engineer with 1 year of hands-on experience building production-grade machine learning solutions that drive real business impact. Based in Rohtak, Haryana, I specialize in designing end-to-end ML pipelines, predictive modeling, and deploying AI systems across cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud.

What I do best is translate complex business problems into high-performance ML models—whether that's classification systems achieving 94%+ accuracy, interactive analytics dashboards used by 50+ stakeholders, or scalable REST APIs handling 10K+ daily requests. I'm equally comfortable working with data preprocessing and feature engineering as I am architecting microservices and optimizing cloud infrastructure.

I'm passionate about solving hard problems collaboratively—I thrive when partnering with product, data science, and engineering teams to deliver impact. With expertise in Python, TensorFlow, PyTorch, and modern DevOps practices, I'm looking for opportunities to apply my technical foundation to challenges that push the boundaries of what's possible with AI.

**✨ Currently:** Available immediately | Graduating with B.Tech in AI & Data Science in 2026

---

## 🚀 What I Do

- 🤖 Build production ML pipelines with 92%+ accuracy
- ☁️ Deploy at scale on AWS, Azure, Google Cloud  
- 📊 Create dashboards used by 50+ stakeholders
- ⚡ Optimize systems (45% query improvement, 50% faster deployments)
- 🔗 Design REST APIs handling 10K+ daily requests

